    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Microdalyellia fairchildi (Graff, 1911) Gieysztor, 1938 (A) Stylet of a specimen from Canada. (B) Stylet of a specimen from Finland. Microdalyellia rossi (Graff, 1911) Gieysztor, 1938 (C – D) Stylets from morphotype 1 animals. (E) Stylet from morphotype 2 animal. (F) Stylet from morphotype 3 animal. (G) Stylet from morphotype 4 animal. (H) Stylet from morphotype 5 animal. (I) Stylet from morphotype 6 animal. (J – K) Stylets from morphotype 7 animals." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207611/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

